#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/family.phtml:128
msgid ""
"Age at first marriage. The mirror axis separates husbands and wives, as "
"shown by the labels at each side. Both sides share the same age bands, so "
"the two distributions can be compared at a glance."
msgstr "Alder ved første ægteskab. Spejlaksen adskiller mænd og kvinder. Etiketterne på begge sider viser det. Begge sider deler de samme aldersbånd. De to fordelinger kan dermed sammenlignes på et øjeblik."

#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/family.phtml:123
msgid "Age at marriage"
msgstr "Alder ved ægteskab"

#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/family.phtml:120
msgid "Age at marriage, duration and the age gap between the spouses"
msgstr "Age at marriage, duration and the age gap between the spouses"

#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/family.phtml:280
msgid ""
"Age difference between consecutive siblings in the same family. Very small "
"gaps (< 1 year) often signal twins or close-spaced births; very large gaps "
"(10+ years) typically reflect second marriages or long intervals."
msgstr ""
"Age difference between consecutive siblings in the same family. Very small "
"gaps (< 1 year) often signal twins or close-spaced births; very large gaps "
"(10+ years) typically reflect second marriages or long intervals."

#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/family.phtml:162
msgid ""
"Age difference between spouses at marriage. Negative values mark couples "
"where the husband was the older partner. Positive values mark couples where "
"the wife was older. Each bar covers a 5-year range. The band labelled 30+ "
"collects every gap of 30 years or more."
msgstr "Aldersforskel mellem ægtefæller på vielsestidspunktet. Negative værdier markerer par, hvor manden var den ældste partner. Positive værdier markerer par, hvor hustruen var ældst. Hver søjle dækker et femårigt interval. Båndet markeret 30+ samler alle forskelle på 30 år eller mere."

#: resources/views/modules/statistics-chart/tabs/life-span.phtml:309
msgid "Age in years at death, longest-lived first"
msgstr "Alder i år ved død, længstlevende først"

